<F P=100> BOSNIA-HERZEGOVINA </F>
<H3> <TI>   Serbs, Muslims Swap POW's Near Brcko </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Serbs, Muslims Swap POW's Near Brcko </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD0906220594 Belgrade TANJUG Domestic Service in 
Serbo-Croatian 2025 GMT 9 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD0906220594 </F>
<F P=104>  Belgrade TANJUG Domestic Service </F>
<F P=105>  Serbo-Croatian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Brcko, 9 Jun (TANJUG) -- The Serbian and Muslim 
sides today swapped a considerable number of civilians and POW's 
in the village of Satorovici, 10 km south of Brcko. The Serbian 
side released 153 Muslim POW's and civilians, while 284 
civilians from the Muslim-held Tuzla region arrived in the 
Srpska republic. 

</TEXT>

