<F P=106> [Article by "r": "Chances of Possible Preelection </F>
Coalitions"] 
  [Text] Bratislava--The FOCUS agency conducted a 
representative public opinion survey from 9 to 23 May 1994, in 
which 2,018 respondents were asked: "There is now much talk 
about the formation of preelection coalitions. Will you please 
say whether you would vote for each of the following possible 
coalitions?" 


