<H3> <TI>   Crvenkovski: Agreement With Greece `Close' </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Crvenkovski: Agreement With Greece `Close' </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   AU1006121594 Skopje MILS-NEWS in English 10 Jun 94 </F>
