European principles. 
  Referring to certain statements by Ioan Alexandru, PNTCD 
[National Peasant Christian-Democratic Party] senator, 
Ambassador Chebeleu said that one cannot talk about a 
discriminatory attitude adopted by Germany in connection with 
Romania joining European institutions. 

