<F P=100> BOSNIA-HERZEGOVINA </F>
<H3> <TI>   Further on Shelling From Croatia </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Further on Shelling From Croatia </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD1206155394 Belgrade TANJUG Domestic Service in 
Serbo-Croatian 1553 GMT 12 Jun 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD1206155394 </F>
<F P=104>  Belgrade TANJUG Domestic Service </F>
<F P=105>  Serbo-Croatian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Excerpts] Brcko, 12 Jun (TANJUG) -- Ivan Todorovic (62) 
was wounded in an artillery attack on Brcko today, the press 
center in Brcko has reported. According to Serb military 
sources, eight 128 mm multiple-rocket launcher missiles were 
fired at 1202 today from positions in Rajevo Selo on the left 
bank of the Sava, from the territory of the Republic of Croatia. 
[passage omitted] Initial reports suggested that the attack 
was launched from Vucilovac, but republic of Srpska army 
observers determined that the missiles were fired from the 
nearby Rajevo Selo in the Republic of Croatia. [passage omitted] 

</TEXT>

