<F P=106> [Unattributed article: "A. Ster Proposed"] </F>
  [Excerpt] [passage omitted] Andrej Ster was born on 12 June 
1958. He graduated from the Ljubljana Law School in 1982. From 
1983 to 1990 he served as a deputy in the Slovene Assembly. At 
the same time he was employed as the secretary of internal 
affairs and a member of the Executive Council of the Kranj 
Community. In the present government he has held the post of the 
state secretary in the Ministry of Internal Affairs. 

